To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private ThreeOutside _threeoutside;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_threeoutside = ThreeOutside(symbol);

// In OnData()
if (_threeoutside.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "threeoutside", _threeoutside.Current.Value);
}
